ey\", \"from\": 4724, \"to\": 4735}, {\"ngram\": \"a father\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4750}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4769}, {\"ngram\": \"her voice\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4784}, {\"ngram\": \"in\\u2026pic.twitter.com/BvRXxlS43y\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4814}, {\"ngram\": \"- Michael R.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4827}, {\"ngram\": \"@ImpactForward)July\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4848}, {\"ngram\": \"TheApplead\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4868}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"musical instruments\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"video games\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"books\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 4927}, {\"ngram\": \"even ancient busts\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4950}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant press\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 4981}, {\"ngram\": \"the splattering\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5020}, {\"ngram\": \"paint\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the press lifted to reveal a sleek new iPad.\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5080, \"end\": 5084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad\", \"score\": 0.9939931505267938, \"rank\": 0.006043149764335439, \"text\": \"iPad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the press\", \"from\": 5041, \"to\": 5050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The intended message, of course, was that Apple's product combines all of those other tangible things into one device.\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5131, \"end\": 5136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5811349906340365e-15, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The intended message\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5114, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"those other tangible things\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"one device\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like theGooglead, however, it simply missed the mark.\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theGooglead\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5224}, {\"ngram\": \"the mark\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the aptly named business-and-technology news outletTechCrunch, the Apple ad sparked a similarly adverse reaction.\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5343, \"end\": 5348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5811349906340365e-15, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the aptly named business-and-technology news outletTechCrunch\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5337}, {\"ngram\": \"a similarly adverse reaction\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it did so for the same reason.\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same reason\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What Apple seems to have forgotten is that it is the things in the real world - the very things Apple destroyed - that give the fake versions of those things value in the first place,\\\" Devin Coldewey wrote for TechCrunch.\", \"from\": 5426, \"to\": 5648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5432, \"end\": 5437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5811349906340365e-15, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://